<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="ja">


<head>
<title>CoHana|ご注文＿写真の撮影</title>

<style>
img{

  border-radius: 0px;
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 700px;
  max-height: 100%;
}
header{
  margin-bottom: 80px;
  margin-top: 0px;
}
.step1-header{
  border-radius: 0px;
  text-align: center;
  width:100%;
  font-weight: bold;
}

.carousel{
  margin: 30px 10px;
}
.carousel-caption{
  bottom: 0;
  border-top:solid 3px gray;
  border-bottom:solid 3px gray;
  border-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;
  padding-top: 0;
  padding-bottom: 0;
  right: 0;
  left:0;
  background: #fffff6;

}
</style>
</head>

<body>
  <header>
    <div class="step1-header bg-danger text-white py-2 my-3 mx-auto">
      CoHanaの使い方
    </div>
  </header>
  <div class="container">

  <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">

    <div class="carousel-inner">
      <div class="carousel-item active">
        <img class="d-block w-100" src="/parent.jpeg" alt="First slide">
          <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-block">
            <h5 class="text-dark mb-0">Step1</h5>
            <p class="text-dark mb-0">子供と一緒にお花の絵を描きます</p>
          </div>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img class="d-block w-100" src="/sketch.jpeg" alt="Second slide">
        <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-block">
          <h5 class="text-dark mb-0">Step1</h5>
          <p class="text-dark mb-0">描いてもらう絵はこんな感じ</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img class="d-block w-100" src="/smartphone.jpeg" alt="Third slide">
        <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-block">
          <h5 class="text-dark mb-0">Step2</h5>
          <p class="text-dark mb-0">写真を下記ボタンよりお選びください</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img class="d-block w-100" src="/formimage.png" alt="Third slide" style="border:solid 2px gray">
        <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-block">
          <h5 class="text-dark mb-0">Step3</h5>
          <p class="text-dark mb-0">あとは注文フォームに入力するだけ</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img class="d-block w-100" src="/download2.jpg" alt="Third slide">
        <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-block">
          <h5 class="text-dark mb-0">Step4</h5>
          <p class="text-dark mb-0">絵をもとにフラワーボックスを作成します</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img class="d-block w-100" src="/family.jpg" alt="Third slide">
        <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-block">
          <h5 class="text-dark mb-0"></h5>
          <p class="text-dark mb-0">大切な人へのギフトにぜひご利用ください</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
      <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
    </a>
    <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
      <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
    </a>
  </div>


  <div style="text-align:center;">
    絵の用意ができた方はこちら
  </div>
<div>
<ul class="picture">
  <li>
<%=link_to("フォルダから選ぶ","/order/file_upload",class:"btn btn-danger btn-lg")%>
</li>
<li>
<%=link_to("今撮影する","/order/take_picture",class:"btn btn-danger btn-lg")%>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

<div class="return">
<%=link_to("戻る","/",class:"btn btn-danger btn-lg")%>
</div>

</div>

<footer class="text-center w-100 text-dark">
    Copyright 2018 Mawi,Inc. All Rights Reserved.
</footer>
</div>
</body>

</html>
